{
  "name": "04 - Extract Best Quotes from Podcast/Presentation",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": { "content": "## Extract Best Quotes via Voice Inflection Analysis\n\nUses the animated quote detection feature to find the most\nexciting/passionate moments in audio by analyzing voice inflection.\n\n**API Features Used:**\n- `animated_quotes=true` \u2014 voice inflection analysis\n- Prosody features: energy, spectral centroid, pitch variation,\n  MFCC variance, zero crossing rate\n- Topic classification into 3 categories\n- Returns top 10 quotes with excitement scores (0.0-1.0)\n- Each quote is exactly 15 seconds with precise timestamps\n\n**Topic categories** are tuned for enterprise/tech content:\n- `current_state` \u2014 how things work today\n- `future_direction` \u2014 roadmap and vision\n- `product_pipeline` \u2014 upcoming features and releases\n\n**Output files:**\n- `.vtt` \u2014 full WebVTT transcript\n- `.json` \u2014 full segments with timestamps\n- `_animated_quotes.txt` \u2014 top 10 quotes report\n- `_animated_quotes.json` \u2014 structured quote data\n\n**Use cases:**\n- Pull best soundbites from podcasts\n- Find highlight clips from presentations\n- Content curation for social media", "color": 4, "width": 430, "height": 500 },
      "id": "note", "name": "Overview", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote", "typeVersion": 1, "position": [200, 20]
    },
    {
      "parameters": { "httpMethod": "POST", "path": "extract-quotes", "responseMode": "responseNode", "options": {} },
      "id": "webhook", "name": "Receive Podcast/Presentation", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook", "typeVersion": 2, "position": [200, 560]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "={{ $env.TRANSCRIPTION_API_URL || 'https://transcript.fluximetry.com' }}/api/v1/jobs",
        "sendBody": true,
        "contentType": "multipart-form-data",
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "parameterType": "formBinaryData", "name": "files", "inputDataFieldName": "data" },
            { "name": "model", "value": "small" },
            { "name": "animated_quotes", "value": "true" },
            { "name": "speaker_diarization", "value": "true" }
          ]
        },
        "sendBinaryData": false,
        "options": { "timeout": 30000 }
      },
      "id": "upload", "name": "Transcribe + Extract Quotes", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest", "typeVersion": 4.2, "position": [450, 560],
      "retryOnFail": true, "maxTries": 3, "waitBetweenTries": 2000
    },
    {
      "parameters": { "values": { "number": [{ "name": "pollCount", "value": 0 }], "string": [{ "name": "jobId", "value": "={{ $json.jobs?.[0]?.job_id || '' }}" }] }, "options": {} },
      "id": "init", "name": "Init", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set", "typeVersion": 3.4, "position": [700, 560]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "={{ $env.TRANSCRIPTION_API_URL || 'https://transcript.fluximetry.com' }}/api/v1/jobs/{{ $('Init').item.json.jobId }}",
        "options": { "timeout": 10000 }
      },
      "id": "poll", "name": "Poll", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest", "typeVersion": 4.2, "position": [950, 560],
      "retryOnFail": true, "maxTries": 3, "waitBetweenTries": 1000
    },
    {
      "parameters": { "conditions": { "conditions": [{ "leftValue": "={{ $json.status }}", "rightValue": "completed", "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" } }] } },
      "id": "done", "name": "Done?", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if", "typeVersion": 2, "position": [1200, 560]
    },
    {
      "parameters": { "conditions": { "conditions": [{ "leftValue": "={{ $json.status }}", "rightValue": "failed", "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" } }] } },
      "id": "failed", "name": "Failed?", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if", "typeVersion": 2, "position": [1200, 810]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "values": {
          "number": [{ "name": "pollCount", "value": "={{ ($('Inc').item?.json?.pollCount ?? $('Init').item.json.pollCount ?? 0) + 1 }}" }],
          "string": [{ "name": "jobId", "value": "={{ $('Init').item.json.jobId }}" }]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "inc", "name": "Inc", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set", "typeVersion": 3.4, "position": [1450, 810]
    },
    {
      "parameters": { "conditions": { "conditions": [{ "leftValue": "={{ $json.pollCount }}", "rightValue": 120, "operator": { "type": "number", "operation": "lt" } }] } },
      "id": "limit", "name": "< 10min?", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if", "typeVersion": 2, "position": [1700, 810]
    },
    {
      "parameters": { "amount": 5, "unit": "seconds" },
      "id": "wait", "name": "Wait", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.wait", "typeVersion": 1.1, "position": [1950, 760]
    },
    {
      "parameters": { "content": "## Quote Results\n\nDownloads the animated quotes JSON which contains:\n- Quote text with timestamps\n- Excitement score (0.0 = monotone, 1.0 = highly animated)\n- Topic category (current_state / future_direction / product_pipeline)\n- 15-second clip boundaries for each quote\n\n**Note:** Topic categories are tuned for enterprise/tech content.\nFor other domains, the categories may need customization.", "color": 2, "width": 350, "height": 180 },
      "id": "note-results", "name": "Results Note", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote", "typeVersion": 1, "position": [1450, 350]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "={{ $env.TRANSCRIPTION_API_URL || 'https://transcript.fluximetry.com' }}/api/v1/jobs/{{ $('Init').item.json.jobId }}/files/{{ $('Poll').item.json.output_files?.find(f => f.name.includes('animated_quotes') && f.name.endsWith('.json'))?.name || $('Poll').item.json.output_files?.find(f => f.name.endsWith('.json'))?.name || 'output.json' }}",
        "options": { "timeout": 30000 }
      },
      "id": "dl-quotes", "name": "Download Quotes JSON", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest", "typeVersion": 4.2, "position": [1450, 560],
      "retryOnFail": true, "maxTries": 2, "waitBetweenTries": 1000
    },
    {
      "parameters": { "respondWith": "json", "responseBody": "={{ JSON.stringify({ status: 'completed', quotes: $json.quotes || [], total_quotes: ($json.quotes || []).length, output_files: $('Poll').item.json.output_files }) }}" },
      "id": "respond", "name": "Return Quotes", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook", "typeVersion": 1.1, "position": [1700, 560]
    },
    {
      "parameters": { "respondWith": "json", "responseBody": "={{ JSON.stringify({ status: 'error', message: 'Quote extraction failed or timed out' }) }}", "options": { "responseCode": 500 } },
      "id": "err", "name": "Error", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook", "typeVersion": 1.1, "position": [1950, 960]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Receive Podcast/Presentation": { "main": [[{ "node": "Transcribe + Extract Quotes", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "Transcribe + Extract Quotes": { "main": [[{ "node": "Init", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "Init": { "main": [[{ "node": "Poll", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "Poll": { "main": [[{ "node": "Done?", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "Done?": { "main": [[{ "node": "Download Quotes JSON", "type": "main", "index": 0 }], [{ "node": "Failed?", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "Failed?": { "main": [[{ "node": "Error", "type": "main", "index": 0 }], [{ "node": "Inc", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "Inc": { "main": [[{ "node": "< 10min?", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "< 10min?": { "main": [[{ "node": "Wait", "type": "main", "index": 0 }], [{ "node": "Error", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "Wait": { "main": [[{ "node": "Poll", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "Download Quotes JSON": { "main": [[{ "node": "Return Quotes", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] }
  },
  "settings": { "executionOrder": "v1" },
  "meta": { "description": "Uses voice inflection analysis to extract the top 10 most excited/animated quotes from a podcast or presentation. Returns quotes with excitement scores, timestamps, and topic categories tuned for enterprise/tech content.", "templateCredsSetupCompleted": true },
  "tags": [{ "name": "transcription" }, { "name": "animated-quotes" }, { "name": "podcast" }, { "name": "content-curation" }]
}